{
  "stem": "2578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry-- from the-- from the German occupation, towards the Russian borders.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the time the ghetto was established and closed, about 50,000 Jews or so left Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Jews had to go in-- into the ghetto, there were about 200,000 of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But no-- none Jews from the outlying areas of Lodz came in to Lodz, except that later on when the ghetto was established.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the ghetto-- when the ghetto was established, from 1940 until 1944, periodically the small towns around Lodz were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, there were ghettos established in those areas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And little by little, the Jews were evacuated from these.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These ghettos were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those were-- that were-- those Jews in these areas around Lodz that were capable of work were shipped in-- into the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the elderly people, sick people and children were sent to Chelmno to be executed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This way, the population in the Lodz ghetto remained at about the same level.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because a lot of Jews living in the ghetto died out, because of hunger and other conditions, epidemics, sicknesses, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they were replaced by the Jews that came in from the adjacent areas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except also for the fact that during those four years, from time to time, orders came in from the German authority that they need a certain amount of people to be sent out from the ghetto, supposedly for work, whether in other areas in Poland or in Germany.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So orders came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They need 2,000 people, people capable to work and with promises of better conditions.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
